strings: <voice_0x01001C59><se_high>Princess Medea: But my stomach's getting full from drinking so much water.
<voice_0x01001C5A><se_high>Princess Medea: I hate to say this, but I think I'm going to have to stop drinking for a while.

<voice_0x01001C5B><se_high>Princess Medea: After I walk for a little bit,
I should be able to drink again... Oh!
